Bad. Ok, I understand, this thing is a TS (a TS is a CAM recording with line sound) so some blurriness is to be expected, but this also suffers from compression artifacts. Other TSes/CAMs outhere have either out-of-sync audio or a video rating of 4 (though I understand this is subjective to commenter) so they are actually worse.

If you know of a better quality version, please post. If not, I will wait for the R5 or the DVD, as not to ruin the movie for me.
